bf88200e-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:

Tap a few dabs of Rose Quartz to the apples of cheeks for a rosy blush. Add a swipe of Opal to the tops of cheekbones for a starlit highlight.

Golden Contour Collection: The ultimate warm-toned trio to achieve luminous, glow-from-within skin. Trace hollows of cheekbones with Amber for a soft, sunkissed tan. Tap a few dabs of Topaz to the apples of cheeks for a warm, rosy peach blush. Add a swipe of Carnelian to the tops of cheekbones for a luminous coral highlight.

Radiant Contour Collection: The essential rosy-hued trio to amplify natural radiance with a soft flush. Trace hollows of cheekbones with Obsidian for a defined deep bronze. Tap a few dabs of Pink Diamond to the apples of cheeks for a neutral pink blush. Add a swipe of Pearl to the tops of cheekbones for a pearlescent peony glow.

bf881d84-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
A ground-breaking Bakuchiol Eye Balm, fully powered by plants.

Harness the power of plant-based ingredients that target all major eye area concerns in one age-defying cream. This multi-correctional concentrate is infused with natural retinol Bakuchiol to brighten and smooth, while micro Hyaluronic Acid restores plumping hydration around the delicate eye area.

Infused with a blend of vibrant floral-derived ingredients, such as Astaxanthin and Turmeric, to create a gorgeous peach hue that instantly evokes brightening benefits and improves the look of dark circles, without leaving visible color on skin.

This product is unscented to protect the sensitive area around the eyes.

Use AM & PM. Dab onto skin around eye area with golden applicator and gently massage. The golden applicator allows for a smooth deposit of product to the delicate eye area with a cooling and soothing massage sensation.

bf881a46-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
A powerful cleansing soap that effectively removes makeup and buildup from cosmetic brushes without harsh chemicals for a beyond-clean application.

Directions: Wet makeup brush with warm water and rub over the soap to create a lather. Gently scrub bristles while rinsing. Rinse brush thoroughly with warm water and repeat as needed. Hold brush downward whenever wet. Remove any excess water from brush. Let brush dry completely. Rinse and remove any excess water from cleansing soap jar. Let dry completely before capping. Recommended cleaning 2-3 times per week.

bf8817bc-0fed-11ef-acf0-36ed3c6c91fc.description:
A powerful natural Retinol (Bakuchiol) concentrate that reduces the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles, smoothing skin texture to amplify anti-aging results.


The percentage in the product title signifies the strength of the concentrated dose of the active ingredient within our formulation. Our Natural Retinol Elixir harnesses an above-average strength of 2% Bakuchiol since it is a naturally derived alternative, which allows it to be a higher concentration and more gentle on the skin.

Apply directly to targeted areas or blend to boost other products. Use AM + PM on freshly cleansed skin. For use as a targeted treatment, apply a generous layer directly to skin.


To boost the efficacy of compatible products, blend a few drops in the palm of your hand to any of the following:


Seeds of Youth Serum
Jojoba Glow Face Oil
Velvet Botanical Moisturizer
Brightening Botanical Eye Balm
Indigo Dream Renewal Cream
